    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Rathman:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "This is in response to your letter dated 16 December 1948,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "subject \"Photographs\", with inclosures, addressed to Major",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "D. J. Grant at this site, concerning photographs taken during",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the month of July 1947 by Mr. William Presley of 218 Illinois",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Avenue, Oak Ridge, Tennessee, of an unidentified object that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "appeared to be flying over Oak Ridge.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Since receipt by Major Grant of the above material, this office",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "has taken steps to secure an evaluation of same by the Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "office of the Chief, Technical Intelligence Division, Intelli-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "gence Department, Air Materiel Command, at Wright-Patterson Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Force Base, Dayton, Ohio. As a result, the following informa-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "tion has been revealed:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "\"When the negative, containing the sphere, is examined",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "by strong incident light, it is noted that the emulsion",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "is raised at that point above the normal level of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "remaining emulsion. This indicates that either a drop",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "of warm water or a drop of developer struck the film at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "this point and rolled down this negative and the succeed-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "ing negative.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "\"To further substantiate this, it will be noted that when",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the two (2) negatives are placed side by side with the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "edges of the film aligned, the so-called \"trail\" is con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "tinuous, that is the two sections match indicating the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "drop rolled on from one negative to the next.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "\"Still further proof is shown on the fogged edge of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "negative containing only the trail. This is proven by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
